intent.user_query: Find products that are frequently sold together (market basket analysis - simplified, find products sold in the same sale).

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT sd1.ProductID AS Product1, sd2.ProductID AS Product2, COUNT(*) AS Frequency FROM fitness_db.SaleDetails sd1 JOIN fitness_db.SaleDetails sd2 ON sd1.SaleID = sd2.SaleID AND sd1.ProductID < sd2.ProductID GROUP BY Product1, Product2 ORDER BY Frequency DESC QUALIFY ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY Frequency DESC) <= 5;

arguments.sql: SELECT sd1.ProductID AS Product1, sd2.ProductID AS Product2, COUNT(*) AS Frequency FROM fitness_db.SaleDetails sd1 JOIN fitness_db.SaleDetails sd2 ON sd1.SaleID = sd2.SaleID AND sd1.ProductID < sd2.ProductID GROUP BY Product1, Product2 ORDER BY Frequency DESC QUALIFY ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY Frequency DESC) <= 5;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
